name: feather your nest necklace- customizable!
description:
how many eggs are in your nest? choose one glass pearl for each of your little birdies & they will be delicately wrapped in silver plated wire. 
choose anywhere from 1-6 eggs in robins egg blue or pretty blush pink. 
the nest hangs from a delicate 18" silver plated brass chain. the lobster clasp can be made either left or right handed.

not a mama? order your necklace with the brown eggs & a leaf charm! 

choose the charm that hangs with your nest {mama bird, hummingbird or leaf} 

make sure to include the following in the message to seller: 
number of eggs, color of eggs, charm, left or right handed clasp and chain length if different from the default.
